<div class="container flex mx-auto mb-4 rounded-lg shadow-lg justify-center bg-gray-100 md:flex-row dark:bg-gray-700 dark:text-white">
 
  <div class="flex flex-col justify-center space-y-8 lg:mt-8 lg:w-4/5 lg:gap-2">
    <h1 class="mx-auto py-4 text-2xl text-center font-bold underline underline-offset-4 lg:text-4xl lg:text-left md:text-lg">
      The Story Behind Aji Tracker
    </h1>

    <div class="flex items-center justify-center w-full space-x-4 md:justify-start">
      <%= image_tag('aji.jpg', class: "rounded-sm shadow-md border-b-4 relative z-10") %>
    </div>

    <p class="mx-auto text-base text-center text-gray-400 lg:text-2xl lg:text-left md:text-sm">
      This app was inspired by my first cat, Aji, a ginger and white furball with a surprisingly particular taste. Unlike most ginger cats, Aji has his own unique preferences, and it took a lot of trial and error to discover that he loves chicken far more than tuna or salmon.
    </p>
    <p class="mx-auto text-base text-center text-gray-400 lg:text-2xl lg:text-left md:text-sm">
      At first, I used a simple Excel sheet to track Aji's meals, hoping to find a pattern. I quickly noticed that if I gave him something he didn't like, he would skip the meal entirely and walk away.
    </p>

    <p class="mx-auto text-base text-center text-gray-400 lg:text-2xl lg:text-left md:text-sm">
      But using Excel for daily manual entry was tedious, and visualizing trends was a challenge. That's why I created Aji Tracker: to easily visualize eating trends over time and organize Aji's favorite foods, ensuring he stays well-fed and happy every day.
    </p>
    <p class="mx-auto text-base pb-4 text-center text-gray-400 lg:text-2xl lg:text-left md:text-sm">
      âœ¨ Ready to give it a try? Sign up and see for yourself.

      If you're interested in learning more about cat eating habits, I highly recommend consulting a professional. I personally found great insights from 
      <a href="https://www.petbuddytraining.com/" target="_blank" class="text-blue-400 underline decoration-2 decoration-blue-400">Pet Buddy Cat Behavior, LLC</a>.
    </p>
  </div>
</div>